To solve this problem efficiently, we can use a hash map (or dictionary) to track occurrences of numbers in the array. This allows us to find pairs with an absolute difference of 
ğ‘˜
k in 
ğ‘‚
(
ğ‘›
)
O(n) time, rather than the 
